description: Music Mainnet - Mavericks is the first ever music collection to be listed in the Bitcoin ecosystem. The collection consists of five short clip 1/1s that represent music from industry leading projects such as Neo Tokyo and Non Fungible Arcade. All music is composed and produced by the Music Mainnet team with the exception of "UAEC" which is a remix of the original music from the legendary UAEC Escape Game that was a part of the Neo Tokyo pre-upload trial.
name: Music Mainnet
